{"tid":172492,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"Juno 隻Words of silence好好聽","createTime":"2017-03-26T02:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T16:15:06.000Z","uid":89349,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d59806e8a68878c5a24d7c1924723e7172667d5","tid":172492,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T02:56:35.000Z","msg":"最愛鐵甲人、酷兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/73Ad80d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F73Ad80d.jpg&h=6b696937&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7c12d7c1e378484dbef9ccf79eda4640f1645ef","tid":172492,"uid":59006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T03:16:07.000Z","msg":"識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無念仲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e52516a7dad65d19fbf3cb641ddcf03c75d70e","tid":172492,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T04:04:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無念仲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54c68e1cae5269584ae4af5883fb24d8a00e2c6","tid":172492,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T04:06:37.000Z","msg":"其實首首都正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成隻碟都係王雙駿監製<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a5a9bed62c9945f7ad1b74a779a30dd2aa190e","tid":172492,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T04:11:12.000Z","msg":"聽緊《燈塔》<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乘一隻白晝的破船<br />\n而突然夜晚<br />\n望見天邊竟有愛情 很像燈塔<br />\n然後會照到我面前<br />\n覺得美麗 照亮了一剎<br />\n給我時間 我可以尋到她<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad19763f60caaf10675a6fb8705254874383ba69","tid":172492,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T08:21:48.000Z","msg":"鐵甲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個旋律好正"},{"pid":"73f7cca4d4b4bb9d54fc0b505374bfc71e019bc2","tid":172492,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T08:28:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鐵甲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個旋律好正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n病態地 沉溺於不開心閱讀那本塊肉餘生<br />\n硬朗地 來用痛成立愛來為你印下蓋印<br />\n<br />\n好一個強壯鐵人 頭破血流 也都不理<br />\n捱得鞭撻 捱得掌摑 化做硬石懷念你<br />\n烙印傷痕太美 穿上了盔甲 盲目愛也未至死<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb89334a403f41c8e2c2678957490cade98eb189","tid":172492,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:49:07.000Z","msg":"不渴望　你不要令我多幾多渴望<br />\n你只要為我點一點火　然後讓我此刻至少可度過<br />\n我可以令你差不多有快樂　我可以為你點一點火<br />\n然後望你輪廓　不講甚麼悲壯　不想甚麼沮喪<br />\n煙圈悄悄墜落煙灰至少將心事証明燃燒過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187d733917c9c2b011ee9135591134312d078634","tid":172492,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:52:30.000Z","msg":"除咗開頭一兩隻碟唔係juno自己意願出嘅碟封面有樣外，我諗呢隻係例外有樣睇"},{"pid":"038822c4e02d7d839400d5466443341a0e99417c","tid":172492,"uid":8204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:52:42.000Z","msg":"鐵甲人真係無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最愛呢隻碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02207c73e948a1aba4dfd02567c3e04395fffa0","tid":172492,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T07:52:13.000Z","msg":"原來係十年前喇已經，咁就老左十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8999d9b6af9cd34dc38156e3f5cc7ed228b845d","tid":172492,"uid":674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T08:01:59.000Z","msg":"呢隻碟係我聽得Juno最多嘅碟<br />\n愈聽愈有味道，由最初得一兩首鍾意到隻隻都鍾意，對我嚟講新歌人渣俾我嘅感覺都係Words Of Silence 2.0嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1771ade3fdbefcb456849683c946918fbc423b7e","tid":172492,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T16:03:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢隻碟係我聽得Juno最多嘅碟<br />\n愈聽愈有味道，由最初得一兩首鍾意到隻隻都鍾意，對我嚟講新歌人渣俾我嘅感覺都係Words Of Silence 2.0嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人渣都ok好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c7068b055f676b9fef6638c05bdf59a5bef567","tid":172492,"uid":49864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T15:52:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢隻碟係我聽得Juno最多嘅碟<br />\n愈聽愈有味道，由最初得一兩首鍾意到隻隻都鍾意，對我嚟講新歌人渣俾我嘅感覺都係Words Of Silence 2.0嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人渣都ok好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得人渣隻碟似 Why 2.0 多啲，都係歪理。"},{"pid":"dcc0df0712d73dd82ad8aceb8782bfd76e95da09","tid":172492,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T16:17:20.000Z","msg":"再聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5747bb5b37310d521604a99b6d3510491e05a646","tid":172492,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}